Privacy Policy

Kasir – Total QRIS respects user privacy and is committed to protecting user data.

Camera Usage
This application uses the camera permission (android.permission.CAMERA) solely to support app features,
such as QRIS scanning or image capture required for transactions.
Camera data is processed locally on the user's device and is not transmitted to any server.

Data Storage
All transaction data and app settings are stored locally on the user's device.
This application does not use a backend server and does not collect personal user data.

Advertising (AdMob)
This app uses Google AdMob to display advertisements.
AdMob may collect certain data in accordance with Google's privacy policy for advertising purposes.
More information can be found at:
https://policies.google.com/privacy

Google Play Services
This application uses Google Play Services, which may collect information as described in Google's privacy policy.

Data Sharing
Kasir – Total QRIS does not share personal user data with third parties.

Security
We take reasonable measures to protect user data by processing all data locally on the device.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.

Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact:
Email: faskhiysoft@gmail.com
